The paper discusses a method for improving the performance of state-of-the-art algorithms in semi-supervised classification and spectral data embedding. These tasks are typically associated with the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
